独家 | 5天建成的“火眼”实验室启动试运行，将为实现“疑似全检测”发挥重要作用。
The "Fireeye" laboratory, built in five days, will play an important role in bringing about "suspected full-scale testing."
黄祺。
Wangqi.
新民周刊                      。
Xinmin Weekly.
新民周刊。
Xinmin Weekly.
深度和角度——这就是我们能做的。
Depth and angle - that's what we can do.
