“火眼”实验室投入运行，将为武汉及周边城市提供充足的检测能力，也将作为“雷神山”、“火神山”、“方舱”等众多抗疫堡垒的前哨，并将为一线员工和疫区人群重返工作岗位提供坚实的科学依据。
The laboratory, which will provide adequate detection capacity for Wuhan and surrounding cities, will also serve as outposts for many battle fortresses, including "Thunder Mountain," "Flaming Mountain" and "Fangcao," and will provide a solid scientific basis for frontline workers and people in affected areas to return to work.
文 | 黄　祺武汉疑似患者未得到诊断的问题，近一两天有望得到缓解。
Wangqi Wuhan suspected patients have not been diagnosed with the problem, nearly a day or two is expected to ease.
这背后，刚刚交付使用的“火眼”实验室将在核酸样本检测环节，发挥很大的作用。
Behind the scenes, the "Fireeye" laboratory, which has just been commissioned, will play a major role in the detection of nucleic acid samples.
程征宇 |摄___2月5日下午，设计检测通量为每日万人份级的新型冠状病毒应急检测实验室——“火眼”实验室正式启动试运行。
At the afternoon of February 5, Flaming Eye, a new coronavirus emergency testing laboratory designed to detect fluxes of 10,000 people a day, was commissioned.
“火眼”实验室由武汉市政府、东湖高新区、中交二航局、上海诺瑞实验室、华大基因联合共建。
The "Fire Eye" lab is jointly built by Wuhan city government, Donghu Hi-tech Zone, Zhongjiao Second Navigation Bureau, Shanghai Nori Laboratory and Huada Gene.
其中，东湖高新区提供场地，华大基因主导设计及运营，中交二航局主导施工，上海诺瑞提供大量实验室装备。
Among them, the East Lake Hi-tech Zone provides the site, Huada gene dominates the design and operation, China Jiaotong two navigation bureau dominates the construction, Shanghai Nori provides a large number of laboratory equipment.
实验室占地面积约为2000平方米。
The laboratory covers an area of about 2000 square meters.
程征宇 |摄1月30日，华大基因完成实验室设计，中交二航局于1月31日正式启动实验室施工，在中交二航局和上海诺瑞的279名员工自愿加班、全力奋战下，仅用5天时间，完成实验室主体施工。
On January 30, Huada completed its lab design. On January 31, the China National Aviation Administration officially launched laboratory construction. With 279 employees at the China National Aviation Administration and Shanghai Nori volunteering overtime and hard work, it only took five days to complete the main body of the laboratory.
“火眼”实验室核心实验区总面积达1000平方米，严格按照P2（生物安全二级）实验室设计，装备华大智造高通量测序整体解决方案和设备；配置30台B2级生物安全柜；批量自动化核酸提取平台配置12台自动化提取设备；同时，配备有配套实验室隔间、样本间、试剂保存间、办公区等，设计检测通量为每日万人份级。
With a total area of 1,000 square meters, the core laboratory test area is designed strictly according to the P2 (biosafety level II) laboratory design, equipped with 30 B2 class biosafety cabinets, 12 automated extraction equipment for batch automated nucleic acid extraction platforms, and equipped with matching laboratory compartments, sample rooms, reagent storage rooms and office areas.
“火眼”实验室投入运行，将为武汉及周边城市提供充足的检测能力，为发热病人的确诊、高危人群的排查、疑似病例的甄别、隔离阳性感染者、保护阴性健康人群提供精准的判断，也将作为“雷神山”、“火神山”、“方舱”等众多抗疫堡垒的前哨，并将为一线员工和疫区人群重返工作岗位提供坚实的科学依据。
The laboratory, which will provide Wuhan and surrounding cities with adequate detection capabilities, will provide accurate diagnosis of febrile patients, screening of high-risk groups, screening of suspected cases, isolation of positive infected persons, and protection of the negative healthy population.
2月6日晚上公布的最新数据，2月5日湖北省共检测样本12277例，其中，武汉市检测样本6500例。
The latest figures, released on the night of Feb. 6, showed 12,277 samples tested in Hubei province on February 5, including 6,500 in Wuhan.
“截至目前，武汉市已有35家机构能开展核酸检测项目，能确保昨天新增的疑似病例今天全部采样检测。
"So far, 35 institutions in Wuhan have been able to carry out nucleic acid testing programs, which can ensure that all the suspected cases added yesterday are sampled today.
”发布会透露，湖北目前共有97家检测机构开展核酸检测检验，中国疾控中心和17个省份的83位实验室检测人员增援湖北，饱和状态下，日检测能力最高可以达到万人份。
A total of 97 testing organizations in Hubei Province have conducted nucleic acid tests, and 83 laboratory testers from China's CDC and 17 provinces have stepped up their efforts to help Hubei province, which has a daily detection capacity of up to 10,000 people at saturation, the conference said.
2月5日，全省共检测样本12277例，其中，武汉市检测样本6500例。
On February 5, 12,277 samples were tested in the province, including 6,500 in Wuhan.
但从另一个数据中我们仍然可以看到接下来湖北省新冠肺炎医疗诊断和救治的压力：截至2月5日24时，湖北省累计追踪密切接触者90997人，尚在接受医学观察64127人。
However, from another data, we can still see the pressure of medical diagnosis and treatment of Xinguan Pneumonia in Hubei Province. As of 2400 hours on February 5, 90,997 people in close contact in Hubei Province had been tracked, and 64127 were still under medical observation.
以上庞大的人群中，很多人都将有检测需求。
Many of these large groups will be in need of testing.
程征宇 |摄昨天（2月6日）晚上，华大基因接受了《新民周刊》采访，介绍了备受瞩目的“火眼”实验室目前的运转情况。
Yesterday evening (February 6), Huada Gene spoke to Xinmin Weekly about the current operation of its eye-catching Eye of Fire lab.
___《新民周刊》：火眼实验室2月5日交付使用，现在已经开始接收检测样本了吗？正式运转是什么时候开始？什么时候可以达到每天万人份的检测量？___华大基因：”火眼”实验室将在武汉市新型肺炎防控指挥部的部署下高效运转，经过2月5日的连夜试运行，2月6日下午，“火眼”实验室的理论通量已达4000人份/日。
When did the test run begin? When will the test run begin? When will the test amount be reached? The Huada Gene: The Flaming Eye Laboratory will operate efficiently under the deployment of the Wuhan New Pneumonia Command.
目前，我们正在进行包括核糖核酸自动化提取设备的调试，以及整个检测流程的优化。
At present, we are including the RNA automatic extraction equipment debugging, as well as the optimization of the entire detection process.
相关试运行程序完备后，我们会根据武汉市新型肺炎防控指挥部的统一部署和实际需求，逐步提升检测通量。
After the relevant trial run procedure is completed, we will gradually improve the detection flux according to the unified deployment and actual requirements of Wuhan New Pneumonia Control Command.
___《新民周刊》：除了量，我们还特别期待速度。
_ _ _ New People's Weekly: In addition to quantity, we are looking forward to speed.
按照最佳的运行状态，一个人的样本检测，最快多少时间能够做完？___华大基因：单个样本通过人工操作进行核糖核酸提取及PCR检测，实验流程约为3小时。
According to the best operating conditions, how much time can a person complete for sample testing? _ _ Huada gene: A single sample is extracted by hand and PCR is detected, and the experimental process is about 3 hours.
但在集中处理大规模样本的检测时，整体完成时间会受到样本信息流、规模化生产排期等多方面的影响。
However, in the centralized processing of large-scale sample testing, the overall completion time will be affected by sample information flow, large-scale production scheduling and so on.
目前，华大基因在接收到疾控中心及医院的检测样本后，保证在24小时内出具检测结果。
At present, Huada Gene after receiving the CDC and hospital test samples, guarantee to produce the test results within 24 hours.
“火眼”实验室配备了华大智造自动化样本制备系统（MGISP-960），可成规模实现样本自动化提取，大大加快限速限通量的核酸提取环节，将整体提升大规模样本的检测速度。
Flame Eye is equipped with a Huada Automated Sample Preparation System (MGISP-960), which enables automatic sample extraction on a large scale, greatly speeding up the process of nucleic acid extraction for speed-limiting fluxes and improving the detection rate of large-scale samples as a whole.
程征宇 |摄___《新民周刊》：大家工作强度是怎样的？人手是不是紧张？___华大基因：实验室需要配备至少150人的团队，以24小时3班轮替的工作方式，才能保障“火眼”实验室每日1万人份的满负荷运转状态。
_ _ _ _ _ _ _ Xinmin Weekly: What's the intensity of everyone's work? Is the manpower tight? _ _ Huada Gene: The laboratory needs a team of at least 150 people to operate at full capacity on a 24-hour, three-shift basis.
___《新民周刊》：实验室有12台自动检测设备，这些设备可以明显帮助检测提速吗？___华大基因：当前新型冠状病毒检测中，疑似样本的病毒核酸提取，多是采用人工操作，人工操作是制约样本检测提速的最大“瓶颈”，也加大了一线医务人员病毒感染的潜在风险。
NEW MINE WEEKLY: There are 12 automatic detection devices in the lab, which can obviously help speed up the detection? _ _ Huada Gene: In the current test for coronavirus, the extraction of viral nucleic acid from the suspected samples is mostly done manually.
通过加载自动化样本制备系统，可以大幅提升疑似样本的病毒核酸提取效率，极大加快新冠病毒的检测及鉴定速度，解决病毒检测速度慢、确诊难的问题，为疫情防控提供了强有力的工具保障。
By loading the automatic sample preparation system, the efficiency of virus nucleic acid extraction can be greatly improved, the detection and identification speed of the new crown virus can be greatly speeded up, the problem of slow virus detection and difficult diagnosis can be solved.
目前，火眼实验室装备的华大智造自动化样本制备系统MGISP-960，已经获得湖北省药品监督管理局注册证书，可实现一站式核酸提取，自动化程度高，上机后完全无人工干预，自动化提取环节仅耗时一小时，可加速大规模人群筛查中的病例检测。
At present, the Huada Automated Sample Preparation System (MGISP-960), equipped by the Fireeye Laboratory, has been certified by Hubei Provincial Drug Administration. It enables one-stop nucleic acid extraction, high automation, no manual intervention at all, and automatic extraction takes only one hour to speed up case detection in mass screening.
这个设备每小时可提取36-96个样本，一人同时操作三台，大大提升人工效率，满足目前高通量筛查的紧急需求。
This facility can extract 36-96 samples per hour, with one person operating three units at a time, greatly improving manual efficiency and meeting the urgent need for current high-throughput screening.
___《新民周刊》：“火眼”实验室的建设只用了5天时间，和常规的实验室相比，有没有做一些简化？___华大基因：按照一般的速度，如此规格的实验室，在物料完备的情况下，至少要3个月的建设时间，我们特别感谢施工方中交二航局和设备支援方上海诺瑞，以及其他合建单位对“火眼”实验室高效建设所付出的巨大努力，他们与华大基因人员连日高强度奋战，让“火眼”实验室在5天时间里严格按照P2（生物安全二级）实验室设计，并达到了试运行要求。
According to Xin Min Weekly: In the last 5 days, has the Flame Eye been built in 5 days, has there been some simplification in comparison with the normal laboratory? At normal speed, it takes at least 3 months to build a laboratory with complete materials.
___《新民周刊》：几天前华大发起“共建万人级病毒检测中心”的倡议，现在“火眼”实验室里有哪些是响应倡议获得的资源？___华大基因：在发出“共建万人级病毒检测中心”的倡议后，“火眼”实验室的建设收到了西安天隆科技有限公司和天根生化科技（北京）有限公司等单位的仪器捐助共4台，以及河南省青少年发展基金会200万元捐款（用于临床检测及相关研发）和IDG资本100万元捐款（用于“火眼”实验室建设）。
What are the resources available in the Flame Eye Laboratories after the launch of the initiative to set up a mass virus testing center? After launching the initiative to set up a mass virus detection center, Flaming Eye received 4 instrument donations from Xi'an Tianlong Technology Co. Ltd. and Tianyuan Biochemical Technology (Beijing) Co. Ltd., as well as a donation of $1 million from Henan Youth Development Foundation for clinical testing and related research and development.
华大基因湖北团队将试剂盒送到黄冈___《新民周刊》：近几天湖北其他地区的疫情正在加重，他们的检测缺口非常大。
Huada Gene Hubei team sent the test kit to Huanggang _ _ _ New People's Weekly. In recent days, other areas in Hubei Province have been experiencing an increase in the number of cases and their detection gap is very large.
华大接下来对这些地区有哪些行动计划？___华大基因：目前华大基因试剂盒已在部分疾控部门和医院开始使用并且储备，疾控和临床评价积极。
What action plans does Huada have for these areas? _ _ Huada Gene: At present, Huada gene test kits have been used in some departments and hospitals and are in reserve, disease control and clinical evaluation are positive.
随着疫情防控进入关键时期，我们全力服务疫情防控需要。
As epidemic prevention and control enter a critical period, we serve the needs of epidemic prevention and control.
希望尽快让武汉、湖北及全国的疑似病例都能第一时间使用试剂盒，让每一位疑似病例能尽快确诊。
It is hoped that Wuhan, Hubei and the national suspected cases can be the first time to use kits, so that every suspected case can be diagnosed as soon as possible.
华大武汉、深圳、天津三地病原交付团队均随时待命，保证检测结果及时交付，为疫情防控提供最快的信息反馈。
Huada Wuhan, Shenzhen, Tianjin three places of the pathogen delivery team are ready to ensure timely delivery of test results for disease prevention and control to provide the fastest information feedback.
征集令“战疫”成败，匹夫有责。
Call for "epidemic" success or failure, the husband is responsible.
《新民周刊》现面向全国征集新冠肺炎采访对象和真实故事：如果你是参与抗击新冠肺炎疫情的医护人员或其家属，我们希望聆听你的“战役”故事，也希望传达你的诉求。
If you are a health care worker or family member involved in the fight against pneumonia, we hope to hear your "battle" story and convey your message.
如果你是确诊、疑似患者本人或家属，我们希望了解你和家人如何“抗疫”的过程，让外界了解你的真实经历。
If you are a confirmed, suspected patient or family member, we would like to know how you and your family have responded to the epidemic and let the outside world know about your true experience.
如果你是疫情严重地区的普通市民，我们希望展现你的乐观，并倾听你所需的帮助。
If you are an ordinary citizen of a highly affected area, we hope to show your optimism and listen to the help you need.
如果你是公共服务人员或各类捐助者，我们希望看到你的“最美逆行”，记录下你的无私。
If you are a public service provider or a variety of donors, we want to see your "most beautiful retrograde" and record your selflessness.
……抗击新冠肺炎疫情，我们诚征对疫情了解的社会各界人士，提供相关线索，说出你的故事，让我们用新闻留存这一切。
To fight the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic, we sincerely invite all sectors of the community to understand the epidemic, provide relevant clues, tell your story, let us use the news to retain all this.
